Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:26.20,COverlay text,,0,0,0,,So he has a nap with his phone still on hold
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:33.50,COverlay text,,0,0,0,,And then after that he does 2 hours of \Nimpressions, holding his phone throughout
