Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:42.41,CDefault,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1018)}Then, after 5 hours of being on hold
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.52,CDefault,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1018)}finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:48.02,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,Ogata-san, I'm sorry. Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:56.29,COverlay text,,0,0,0,,Nedate suddenly hangs up and \Nstarts preparing to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:22:00.60,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,Staff) He hung up, he hung up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:05.54,CDefault,,0,0,0,,Woken up by the staff,\NOgata rushes to confront him
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.54,CDefault,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1018)}And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:12.74,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:14.28,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:16.68,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,It's not about what I'm doing
