Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:19.05,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,It's 3:10am you know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.12,0:22:22.12,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,Staff) Why didn't you hang up the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:24.86,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,I was waiting and creating impressions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:28.23,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,I wrote all these impressions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:31.16,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,There's so much here. Woah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:32.70,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,Were you really watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:35.10,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,Only the first half. I was asleep for the second
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:37.80,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,Sleeping?Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:43.07,CDefault,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1018)}And so, the Ogata squad should not be underestimated
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:43.07,COverlay text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,246)}On-hold challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:43.07,COverlay text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(559,874)}Ogata & Nedate\N\N\N\N\N\NHaraguchi & Kasuga\N\N\N\N\NFujimoto & Nadal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:46.08,CDefaultGreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1018)}Yes, that's all from us
