Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:52.92,DefaultGreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(255,1018)}But Kasuga-san's 3 \Nhours was long too
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:54.92,CDefaultAqua,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1018)}But if Haraguchi hadn't given up there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:56.92,DefaultAqua,,0,0,0,,{\pos(675,898)}he'd do it forever
