Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:58.92,CDefault,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1018)}Yes.\NBecause I was told to wait
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.92,0:23:00.86,DefaultGreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(255,1018)}What goes through your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(415,778)}Well, it's as I said...
