Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:15.21,CDefaultGreen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,898)}Yes more ecstatic the longer it goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(675,1018)}"I'm waiting!"
