Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.18,0:24:46.38,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,Staff) How about from people you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.38,0:24:48.49,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,People I don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.49,0:24:51.49,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,People I don't remember... Wait a moment
