Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.29,0:25:19.63,COverlay text 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1092,792)}Sorry. Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.65,0:25:24.07,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,I didn't think we'd disappoint people so soon after winning
