Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.37,0:26:06.31,BontanWebsite,,0,0,0,,{\pos(288,705)}The "Bontan" is a large fruit that was sent 230 years ago as a\Nthank you for helping a Chinese ship that had\N washed ashore off the coast of Akune.\N\NHave fun harvesting the famous Akune Bontan. \NYou will also be able to try your hand at processing.
