Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.83,0:26:10.33,DefaultAqua,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1012,379)}No, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.33,0:26:14.05,COverlay text,,0,0,0,,And then we checked a local newspaper too...
