Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.51,0:26:21.18,CDefault,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,838)}And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.18,0:26:24.18,CDefault,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,838)}We had an announcer read it out in a news report-style for us
