Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.46,0:28:21.20,Overlay text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(393.9485294117647,1042)}Wow, he's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.30,0:28:24.23,COverlay text,,0,0,0,,We've confirmed he's asleep by checking his brainwaves
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.23,0:28:28.69,COverlay text,,0,0,0,,so will leave it like this for a while
